      "title": "Risk management",
      "description": "Describe critical risks, uncertainties or difficulties related to the implementation of your project, and your measures/strategy for addressing them.\n\nIndicate for each risk (in the description) the impact and the likelihood that the risk will materialise (high, medium, low), even after taking into account the mitigating measures.\n\nNote: Uncertainties and unexpected events occur in all organisations, even if very well-run. The risk analysis will help you to predict issues that could delay or hinder project activities.",
